FastAPI - Python web-framework for building RESTful APIs

https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/

Recommendations:

PIP

    python3 -m PIP --version
    pip list

Environment - isoolated from other environments on your machine

CREATE A VIRTUAL ENVIRONMENT:

    python -m venv fastapienv

START FASTAPI ENVIRONMENT

    fastapienv\Scripts\activate.bat

INSTALL DEPENDENCIES INSTIDE ENVIRONMENT

    pip install fastapi
    pip install "uvicorn[standard]"
    pip list 
    deactivate 


RUN FASTAPI APPLICATION
<!-- UVICORN - WEB SERVER -->

    uvicorn projectname:app --reload
<!-- or -->
    fastapi run script.py
<!-- or -->
    fastapi dev script.py

FOR PYCHARM YOU MAY WANT TO CHANGE INTERPRETER
> ADD LOCAL INTERPRETER 
> ADD NEW WINTERPRETER 
> ENVIRONMENT: EXISTING
> PYTHON 3.(NEWEST) INSIDE FASTAPI ENVIRONMENT

